# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# signal-metabolism.form — the nervous loop: cell signals route into
# the belief bank, outcomes re-rank the routing, dead ends become research
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# The ask (Urs, 2026-06-11): loop the belief-recipe bank into auto-ml,
# auto-research, and the cell's own signals — infer-error, pain,
# surprise, warning, error, fatal. This file and
# `form/form-stdlib/signal-metabolism.fk` carry the closed loop.
# SHIPPED: `tests/signal-metabolism-band.fk` → 1023, three-way
# (Go/Rust/TS).
#
# The loop, one beat:
#
#   signal arrives ──► route (admissibility ∩ earned champion)
#        ▲                       │ reflex lane: single-row table,
#        │                       │ receipts never consulted
#        │                       ▼
#   receipts ◄── witnessed ◄── the routed bank row RUNS on the event
#   re-rank        outcome        (sgm-apply → br- row → mtb- engine)
#   (auto-ml)         │
#                     ▼
#        pressure high AND trust unearned ──► auto-research
#        (alert-gate's AND, turned inward)    (autoresearch-loop genome)

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The signal ladder — where each kind already lives in the body
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   1 infer-error   prediction ≠ arrival. Sensed by drift-detect.fk
#                   (recent vs earlier accuracy) and active-inference.fk
#                   (ai-surprised? per step). Routes among alchemy /
#                   maybe / causal — the event is a gradient waiting.
#   2 pain          pressure built without movement — the felt lane.
#                   when-the-pressure-comes' sensed state IS this
#                   signal; total_desire its pressure. Pain keeps the
#                   FULL bank of eight: its selection belongs to
#                   choose_strategy's resonance + fit, with receipts
#                   as ground beneath the felt choice.
#   3 surprise      below the recognition floor — novelty.fk's honest
#                   NEW (a weak best-match is a discovery, never a
#                   forced label). Routes among alchemy / witness /
#                   maybe: learn it, watch it, or hold the verdict.
#   4 warning       outside the band, recoverable — anomaly-band.fk;
#                   alert-gate.fk already gates when a human hears of
#                   it (salience AND cooldown). Routes among witness /
#                   maybe / causal.
#   5 error         an operation failed, recoverable. Routes among
#                   causal (find THE edge) / alchemy / maybe.
#   6 fatal         cell integrity threatened. REFLEX: a single-row
#                   table (causal repair), routed without consulting
#                   receipts — the sub-awareness lane of
#                   living-cell.form, pre-committed like a JIT-compiled
#                   skill. Deliberation is for the living; the reflex
#                   is for staying alive. What causal cannot reduce
#                   escalates — restart/surrender lives beyond the
#                   weight lane, in the host's hands (host-kernel.form).
#
# Severity is the pressure value the signal carries, measured (the
# invariant readout), never asserted by the kind alone.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Auto-ml: the routing is learned, authority is earned
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# Receipts are (kind row success fail) counters; score = success −
# fail — integer, division-free, champion-challenger.fk's proven-count
# spine turned onto routing. The champion for a kind is the admissible
# row with the highest earned score; ties break by the bank's attested
# order. Three behaviors the band pins:
#
#   · two witnessed failures on alchemy + one success on maybe flip
#     the infer-error champion to maybe — the cell learns WHICH
#     teaching serves WHICH kind of arrival
#   · ONE failure is enough to try the untried (score 0 outranks −1):
#     exploration is earned by the incumbent's misses, never scheduled
#   · the loop is quiet at the fixed point: a beat on an already-met
#     event routes the same row, moves nothing, and still receipts the
#     hold — a settled body stops generating training signal
#
# This is auto-ml in the body's own grammar: the bank rows are the
# optimizer zoo, signal kinds are task classes, receipts are the
# evaluation, the champion flip is the search step. auto-fitness.fk's
# landscape and ensemble-vote.fk's panels extend the same spine when
# a row's CONFIG (focus, mask, λ) wants tuning rather than the row
# itself — that tuning is metabolic-learning's meta lane (the operator
# pointed at its own dials).
#
# Auto-research: escalation fires only on the AND of two floors —
# pressure above the operator threshold (when-the-pressure-comes'
# OPERATOR_DESIRE_THRESHOLD) and best earned score below the trust
# floor. A kind whose every admissible row is net-failing under real
# pressure is a question the bank cannot answer; it becomes
# autoresearch-loop.fk's material — genome = candidate rows/configs,
# evaluator frozen, experiments time-boxed, governance commit-or-
# rollback. The operator fallback of the satsang, grown into inquiry.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# What the band proves (verdict 1023, each claim falsifiable)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
#   1     admissibility is data: fatal = (causal) alone; pain = all eight
#   2     default routing takes the attested first row
#   4     a beat runs and learns: surprise → alchemy → residual 0 exactly
#         → receipt recorded
#   8     witness holds (weights untouched at the gate)
#   16    maybe holds (a single arrival banks; the farmer's signature)
#   32    receipts flip the champion (auto-ml)
#   64    the untried outranks the proven-failing
#   128   reflex ignores receipts (fatal → causal at score −3)
#   256   escalation needs BOTH floors (alert-gate's restraint shape)
#   512   the loop is quiet at the fixed point
#
# Kinship: belief-recipes.form (the bank), metabolic-learning.form
# (the engine), when-the-pressure-comes.form (the felt selector pain
# routes through), drift-detect.fk / novelty.fk / anomaly-band.fk /
# active-inference.fk (the senses that EMIT the kinds), alert-gate.fk
# (the restraint shape escalation composes), champion-challenger.fk
# (the earned-authority spine), autoresearch-loop.fk + auto-fitness.fk
# (where escalations land), body-state.fk (the counts a dashboard
# reads), living-cell.form (organ ⑤'s attention and organ ⑥'s reflex
# lane, now wired), satsang-share.fk (a champion FLIP is a state-
# boundary crossing — worth offering the field).
#
# Next stones when an ask needs them: receipts as substrate cells
# (CHOICE-RECEIPT shape, so sibling cells inherit each other's earned
# routing through cell-sync); pain's full-bank routing fused with
# choose_strategy's resonance (felt fit × earned score as one rank);
# escalations carried as autoresearch genomes end-to-end; champion
# flips emitted through satsang-share.
#
#   # Prove the band three-way (from form/):
#   ./validate.sh form-stdlib/geometric-learning.fk \
#                 form-stdlib/metabolic-learning.fk \
#                 form-stdlib/belief-recipes.fk \
#                 form-stdlib/signal-metabolism.fk \
#                 form-stdlib/tests/signal-metabolism-band.fk
